# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:10
translate portuguese millssurface2_73dfd7de:

    # pc "How long have you been a lawyer?"
    pc "Há quanto tempo é advogada?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:12
translate portuguese millssurface2_871f3aec:

    # bs "Now, [pcname], that's dangerously close to asking me how old I am."
    bs "Ora, [pcname], isso é perigosamente próximo de me perguntar quantos anos tenho."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:13
translate portuguese millssurface2_8ed9a81d:

    # pc "Sorry Mrs. Mills, I didn't mean anything by it."
    pc "Desculpe, Sra. Mills, não tive qualquer intenção."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:14
translate portuguese millssurface2_3b5d4f88:

    # bs "I know you didn't. It's alright."
    bs "Eu sei que não teve. Não faz mal."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:16
translate portuguese millssurface2_99be8058:

    # bs "I've been a lawyer for 30 years. Right out of college, I became the assistant for a public defender."
    bs "Sou advogada há 30 anos. Logo ao sair da faculdade, tornei-me assistente de um defensor público."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:17
translate portuguese millssurface2_362f6c85:

    # bs "Then I became a public defender myself for several years before finally opening up my own practice here with Mr. Gonzales."
    bs "Depois, tornei-me eu própria defensora pública durante vários anos, antes de finalmente abrir o meu próprio escritório aqui com o Sr. Gonzales."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:18
translate portuguese millssurface2_a1f0abc1:

    # bs "I've done pretty well for myself in that time."
    bs "Saí-me bastante bem nesse período."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:19
translate portuguese millssurface2_0606d24e:

    # bs "I do miss being a public defender sometimes though, fighting for justice and all that."
    bs "No entanto, às vezes sinto falta de ser defensora pública, de lutar pela justiça e tudo isso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:20
translate portuguese millssurface2_c5a96b7d:

    # bs "But that was the younger days. I had more passion for it back then."
    bs "Mas isso foi nos tempos de juventude. Naquela altura, tinha mais paixão por isso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millssurface2.rpy:21
translate portuguese millssurface2_13c6bfaf:

    # bs "The pay is much better doing what I do now."
    bs "O salário é muito melhor fazendo o que faço agora."

